show.description: The cold-blooded Alpha King, Logan, meets the naturally alluring she-wolf Anya. But Logan, with his solitary nature, resists letting Aniya get close. The forbidden love between beauty and beast breeds desire amid reluctance, as both sides gradually fall into the depths of destined love.
